gpt3.5_zero_shot.prompt: Give me the most cited papers for each year from 2014 to 2023.
gpt3.5_zero_shot.sql_query:
SELECT p.year, p.title, p.citation_count
FROM papers p
WHERE p.year BETWEEN 2014
AND 2023
AND p.citation_count = (SELECT MAX(p2.citation_count)
FROM papers p2
WHERE p2.year = p.year)
ORDER BY p.year
